			<div id="post-235" class="hentry p1 post publish author-katt category-drawing tag-skerple y2010 m12 d31 h06">
    			<h1 class="entry-title">Skerple Friday: Crab, why do you skerp?</h1>
<div class="entry-meta"><span class="author vcard">By <a class="url fn n" href="/author/admin/" title="View all posts by Katt">Katt</a></span><span class="meta-sep"> | </span><span class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2010-12-31T10:53:55-0400">December 31, 2010</abbr></span></div><!-- .entry-meta -->
				<div class="entry-content">
<p>There&#8217;s like two feet of snow here, and it&#8217;s probably going to be hanging around and growing increasingly grungy until mid-March. I hate winter. So I decided to draw a beach scene.</p>
<p><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/skerple-smokingcrabs.png"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/skerple-smokingcrabs1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-237" title="skerple-smokingcrabs" src="/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/skerple-smokingcrabs1.png" alt="" width="436" height="440" /></a></a></p>
<p>Except&#8230; Crabs, what are you doing?! <a href="http://soundcloud.com/isilence/crab-why-do-you-smoke">Why do you smoke</a>? You&#8217;re crabs! And you&#8217;re polluting the air and the beach!</p>
<p>I doodled a drug-awareness scene from the eighties, too. Growing up in the eighties meant being constantly vigilant of cool kids who would stop at nothing to get you to take drugs.</p>
<p><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/skerple-wantsomedrugs.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-238" title="skerple-wantsomedrugs" src="/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/skerple-wantsomedrugs.png" alt="" width="450" height="466" /></a></p>
<p>And then they&#8217;d show you all their drugs, which would be, like, a beer, a cigarette, assorted pills, and some weird stuff that they don&#8217;t explain and you wouldn&#8217;t know what to do with.</p>
<p><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/skerple-justonedrug.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-239" title="skerple-justonedrug" src="/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/skerple-justonedrug.png" alt="" width="450" height="311" /></a>I get the sense I&#8217;ve doodled about the hilarious 80s drug videos before, but I don&#8217;t think I have. I think it&#8217;s just something I like making fun of, but hadn&#8217;t skerped to paper yet.</p>

									</div>
				<div class="entry-utility"><span class="cat-links">This entry was posted in <a href="/category/drawing/" title="View all posts in drawing" rel="category tag">drawing</a></span><span class="tag-links">  and tagged <a href="/tag/skerple/" rel="tag">skerple</a></span>. Bookmark the <a href="/2010/12/skerple-friday-crab-why-do-you-skerp/" title="Permalink to Skerple Friday: Crab, why do you skerp?">permalink</a>. Comments are closed, but you can leave a trackback: <a class="trackback-link" href="/2010/12/skerple-friday-crab-why-do-you-skerp/trackback/" title ="Trackback URL for your post" rel="trackback">Trackback URL</a>.</div><!-- .entry-utility -->
